def is_prime(n):
    if n == 1:

    if n == 2:

    if n % 2 == 0:

    """Transform high humidity into safe level of heat index in India."""
    
    # Define thresholds for each safety level 
    safety_levels = [0, 30, 60, 80]
    
    # Use if else statement to check which safety level 
    # the current temperature and humidity fall under
